title: Violent J - The Shining [2008][@320k]
description:
The Shining is the second solo album of American rapper Joseph Bruce, better known as Violent J. It was given away at the gathering of the juggalos 2008. A new copy with seven new songs is set to be Released on April 28, 2009. It is the rapper's second full-length album, following the 2003 extended play Wizard of the Hood.
